com.bmd.jrt.invocation

Class TemplateInvocation<INPUT,OUTPUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmd.jrt.invocation.TemplateInvocation<INPUT,OUTPUT>
  • Type Parameters:
    INPUT - the input data type.
    OUTPUT - the output data type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Invocation<INPUT,OUTPUT>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleInvocation, TunnelInvocation

    public abstract class TemplateInvocation<INPUT,OUTPUT>
extends Object
implements Invocation<INPUT,OUTPUT>
    Empty abstract implementation of a routine invocation.

    This class is useful to avoid the need of implementing all the methods defined in the interface.

    Created by davide on 9/11/14.
